Title: An Act Changing the Name of Ondoy Elementary School in the Municipality of Ibajay, Province of Aklan, to Honorable Teodolfo S. Suñer Memorial Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 672
An Act Changing the Name of Ondoy Elementary School in the Municipality of Ibajay, Province of Aklan, to Honorable Teodolfo S. Suñer Memorial Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Ondoy Elementary School located in the Municipality of Ibajay, Province of Aklan, is hereby changed to Honorable Teodolfo S. Suñer Memorial Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
